    "description": "<p>You can spend <strong>1 AP</strong> and <strong>1 SP</strong> to attempt to <strong>Taunt </strong>all enemies within 5 Spaces.</p><p><span >Make an <strong >Attack Check</strong>, <strong >Influence</strong> <strong >Check</strong> or <strong >Intimidation Check </strong>(your choice)</span><strong> </strong>contested by each target’s <strong>Mental Save</strong>.</p><p><strong>Contest Success:</strong> Each creature you beat is <strong> @UUID[Compendium.dc20rpg.rules.JournalEntry.x06moaa9pWzbdrxB.JournalEntryPage.5b8703add31783de]{Taunted}</strong> by you until the end of your next turn.</p><p> </p><p><span ><strong><span >Technique Enhancements</span></strong></span></p><ul><li><strong>Legendary Taunt:</strong> <strong>(2 SP)</strong> Any damage dealt by <strong>@UUID[Compendium.dc20rpg.rules.JournalEntry.x06moaa9pWzbdrxB.JournalEntryPage.5b8703add31783de]{Taunted} </strong>enemies is halved against any creatures other than you.</li></ul>",
